### Template APIs

### Get all templates
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates

### Create a new template
POST http://localhost:3001/api/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Summer Sale Template",
  "structure": {
    "hero": "Hero Banner",
    "products": "Product Grid",
    "footer": "Standard Footer"
  }
}

